New Records: Bas de Leede scored the match-winning runs and took 2 wickets
Key Match Events: Namibia lost 3 wickets inside the Powerplay
Netherlands got off to a flier thanks to Vikramjit Singh and Max O'Dowd
Bas de Leede steadied the ship and saw Netherlands home
Max O'Dowd was run out by Gerhard Erasmus
Post-Match Reflections: Scott Edwards said they don't wanna be known as the team that leaves it late but is stoked with the win
Gerhard Erasmus said they could not keep things tight in the field which made it easier for the opposition
Miscellaneous Highlights: Vikramjit Singh scored 30 runs and hit 2 sixes
Bas de Leede scored 30 runs and hit 1 four
Others: David Wiese cut himself on the forehead during the match
Jan Frylinck bowled a maiden over
